{"build_type":"executable","description":"Static dangling-call audit. Reads {\"roots\":[dir,...]} from stdin, enumerates the package universe and builds the function index (name -> defining path), then reports every function_invocation whose invocation_name resolves to no defined function in the universe. Emits {dangling:[{function,call}], dangling_count, packages_scanned}. Non-gating: a build-time consistency gate at the source level (catches a missed rename or typo as a clean report, before the compiler would segfault on the unresolved call). Run it after a mass rename and before reconcile; zero dangling = the graph is internally consistent. Reuses read_all_of_stdin, decode_entire_source_building_document, locate_named_member_inside_mapping, enumerate_universe_packages, build_function_index, begin_empty_sequence_document_value, count_members_inside_container_value, scan_each_package_for_dangling_calls, begin_empty_mapping_document_value, attach_named_member_inside_mapping, add_number_to_object, emit_result_object_onto_standard_output.","module_name":"report-dangling-invocation-references-record","package_name":"report-dangling-invocation-references-record","function_definitions":{"report-dangling-invocation-references-record":{"return_type":"i64","parameter_definitions":[{"parameter_name":"__argc","parameter_type":"i64"},{"parameter_name":"__argv","parameter_type":"i64"}],"execution_instructions":[{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"zero","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"s_roots","variable_type":"str","assignment_operation":"string","source_target":"roots"},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"s_dangling","variable_type":"str","assignment_operation":"string","source_target":"dangling"},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"s_dcount","variable_type":"str","assignment_operation":"string","source_tar